  <brief_title>Analgesic Efficacy of Bilateral Superficial Cervical Plexus Block in Robot-assisted Endoscopic Thyroidectomy Using a Transaxillary Approach</brief_title>
  <official_title>Analgesic Efficacy of Bilateral Superficial Cervical Plexus Block in Robot-assisted Endoscopic Thyroidectomy Using a Transaxillary Approach</official_title>
